{"id": "1215320588323790889", "channel_id": "1215320588323790889", "type": 0, "author_id": "526316195935420417", "author_name": "hiroki2222", "author_bot": false, "content": "如標題，在使用拉蒙娜時，正常拉蒙娜的女王之劍（消耗算力3）或是環形拉蒙娜的熵增逆轉（消耗算力3）必定會在經過數回合後卡牌突然消失，目前發現只有拉蒙娜消耗算力為3的卡牌必定消失的情況，而且大機率出現在最終boss戰，請問這是個bug還是有一些我沒有注意到的規則呢？望解答。\n\n一開始是在打有融卡的關卡發現這個問題，但後來發現沒有融卡的關卡也有這個問題，目前發現深潛最後boss和進行環形拉蒙娜的劇情boss戰時就出現了這個狀況，持續了一周了，我用安卓和iphone開了兩個號持續遊玩，目前兩個號都出現了同一問題。\n\n現附圖", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T15:30:07.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1215320590177542284", "filename": "IMG_0727.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 582808, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215320588323790889/1215320590177542284/IMG_0727.jpg?ex=6a00a480&is=69ff5300&hm=92b3a30ce8392d5022ee246d0a8655cc5b7d0ebe88699856737de61238c344b6&"}, {"id": "1215320590550962256", "filename": "IMG_0726.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 381417, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215320588323790889/1215320590550962256/IMG_0726.jpg?ex=6a00a480&is=69ff5300&hm=55cb26902d9dcb470a1c07612b899c5b2ac3237a5ff328f9582e30f5741607f8&"}, {"id": "1215320597299462194", "filename": "IMG_0725.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 380951, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215320588323790889/1215320597299462194/IMG_0725.jpg?ex=6a00a481&is=69ff5301&hm=2630a0ee5c3176bb945a0f98962908fdf82b69aa1df582e484ca5d5d9df44ef4&"}, {"id": "1215320598084063254", "filename": "IMG_0729.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 442036, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215320588323790889/1215320598084063254/IMG_0729.jpg?ex=6a00a482&is=69ff5302&hm=e8e5e848463428add7e3b62ad4a0d1ad3bfc3f877fe4f841b828d1675093905c&"}, {"id": "1215320598759211090", "filename": "IMG_0728.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 332490, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215320588323790889/1215320598759211090/IMG_0728.jpg?ex=6a00a482&i