{"id": "1215271016427692082", "channel_id": "1215271016427692082", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，每次開技鑰令的順序都不太一樣，\n需要費神找一下想要的鑰令在哪裡，\n在鑰令越來越多的情況下希望能做到固定位置，\n辛苦了！", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T12:13:08.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1215271017283461180", "filename": "2024-03-07_201142.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 787896, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215271016427692082/1215271017283461180/2024-03-07_201142.png?ex=6a007655&is=69ff24d5&hm=d6cca5db704f0a99e8029c8821adef5624ba26aff701ef49a1e825217612388e&"}, {"id": "1215271017883238470", "filename": "2024-03-07_201114.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 783795, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215271016427692082/1215271017883238470/2024-03-07_201114.png?ex=6a007655&is=69ff24d5&hm=a84c3f43ec334467f79e6c4565fe51c579acdcbf8861c2ffb9862dc002dbf226&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215271016427692082", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」環形拉蒙娜狂氣爆發的鑰令順序問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1215358222135992440", "channel_id": "1215358222135992440", "type": 0, "author_id": "526316195935420417", "author_name": "hiroki2222", "author_bot": false, "content": "請留意影片右上角，角色圖片和造物重疊了(⁠>⁠_<⁠)\n\n發現問題關卡在圖一", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T17:59:40.421000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1215358224056721458", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-03-08-01-52-29-271_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 166591, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215358222135992440/1215358224056721458/Screenshot_2024-03-08-01-52-29-271_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=6a00c78c&is=69ff760c&hm=a12ee67bf1012465fb07db67a1925025109297f0827d579ea1b8f0d836c62eef&"}, {"id": "1215358225277390970", "filename": "VID_20240308_015148.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 13457472, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215358222135992440/1215358225277390970/VID_20240308_015148.mp4?ex=6a00c78d&is=69ff760d&hm=447bf252cf084dce5a529af351ecce5c514f154af5d6f56af862c6351e0a36d0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215358222135992440", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」戰鬥中圖片疊位問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1215333250256474194", "channel_id": "1215333250256474194", "type": 0, "author_id": "743818603903713330", "author_name": "sam511011", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛才用深海隊伍打困難6-3，開完狂氣爆發，點選四人Q圖可看見回合結束額外追打幾次觸手，但實際上不會追打。\n\n以下圖片皆為重打6-3時的情況。前兩張附圖是我只開墨菲，可以看到觸手應該要打4下，然而最終只打3下（第一張圖可能看不出來，最前面有個只剩29血的敵人，後面敵人所受傷害為78×2×1.5=234，可知觸手只打3次）\n\n後兩張是我下一回合開圖魯，敵人最後所受傷害只有360，可知觸手只打360/72=5次\n\n這兩個例子都有觸發界域精通，所以才多追打一次，如果沒觸發，就沒有任何額外的追打。多虧這個bug，我6-3王關差了一些傷害，最後還是用了應急靈知體，可喜可賀🫠\n\n由於手機沒有遊戲錄影功能，僅能提供圖片佐以文字說明，較不直觀還請見諒。另外，我還沒測試這個bug是主線才有還是所有關卡都會發生（但我今天懶得打關卡了...明天再說）。如果有人發生類似情況，還請幫忙提供資訊QQ", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T16:20:26.661000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1215333251296534548", "filename": "Screenshot_20240308-000142385.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 165431, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215333250256474194/1215333251296534548/Screenshot_20240308-000142385.jpg?ex=6a00b04a&is=69ff5eca&hm=3cec96c53a3ef8bbe2823c1cf2f5c7e6e9634f04b304aaa2f228ded5f55a464d&"}, {"id": "1215333251594453082", "filename": "Screenshot_20240308-000205350.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 123813, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215333250256474194/1215333251594453082/Screenshot_20240308-000205350.jpg?ex=6a00b04a&is=69ff5eca&hm=6ee9dc562bc09aab1923691d7f67b52db3d3f3fcde4ddb8ef02022ea0ad50d2a&"}, {"id": "1215333251992920114", "filename": "Screenshot_20240308-000759122.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 158047, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215333250256474194/1215333251992920114/Screenshot_20240308-000759122.jpg?ex=6a00b04b&is=69ff5ecb&hm=154e440fc6a46e6828e7ec632877ae68ad99884b07bec9761b98d907322604af&"}, {"id": "1215333252416671814", "filename": "Screenshot_20240308-000808109.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 123537, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215333250256474194/1215333252416671814/Screenshot_20240308-000808109.jpg?ex=6a00b04b&is=69ff5ecb&hm=6982d7e1881788b3437b4107cb082d7811ee70c486bbf3a28f60183edf43fea1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215333250256474194", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」深海界域 狂氣爆發後未有額外的觸手攻擊次數", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1215134085631189032", "channel_id": "1215134085631189032", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，主要是想事後分析或分享通關影片，\n雖然可以自己手機常駐開啟錄影，\n但中間可能會一直凹重新戰鬥，\n一錄下去說不定就半小時手機超燙，\n\n希望遊戲內能有replay重播通關Boss戰的的功能，\n最好還可以作為紀念儲存，時不時拿出來回味分享(炫耀)\n~~作為吃瓜群眾也可以看到其他大佬們是如何群魔亂舞的~~", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T03:09:02.114000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-07T03:10:11.857000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215134085631189032", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」希望能有戰鬥紀錄replay功能", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
